nars.util.data.map

Class FastPutsArrayMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • nars.util.data.map.FastPutsArrayMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class FastPutsArrayMap<K,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
implements java.io.Serializable
    Optimised for very small data sets, allowing compact size and fast puts at the expense of O(n) lookups. This implementation may store duplicate entries for the same key. TODO: explain more.
